---
// Hero.astro
---

<section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Eyebrow badge -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-50 text-brand-500 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 border border-brand-100">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-500"></span>
      In development
    </div>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-semibold text-gray-900 leading-tight tracking-tight max-w-3xl">
        Silicon design, accelerated.
    </h1>

    <!-- Sub-headline -->
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-500 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
      Chip design has outgrown its tools. Verion is rebuilding the EDA stack from first principles — a GPU-native, intelligent platform that brings the speed and flexibility of modern software to the world's most complex engineering challenge.
    </p>

    <!-- USP pills -->
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
        <span class="text-brand-500 font-mono text-xs font-semibold">10x–50x</span> faster than CPU simulators
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
        On-premise or cloud
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
        Full debug traces &amp; coverage
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
      <a
        href="#waitlist"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-brand-500 text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-600 transition-colors"
      >
        Try Verion on your next regression
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#product"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-gray-700 font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
      >
        See how it works
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
